Description
This set of documents describes the multi-page storytelling dashboard (Streamlit + Plotly) for China’s transformation between 2000 and 2020. Each page document explains the narrative intent and details of every chart, including variables, encodings, annotations, and interpretation.

Data & Methods
- Data source: primarily World Bank indicators; years: 2000–2020.
- Visuals: Plotly (Express and Graph Objects), consistent themes, margins, and legends.
- Interactivity: Streamlit filters (decade/period), sliders, and navigation.
